---
title: Asian-Style Grilled Beef Koftas with Mango-Cucumber Slaw and Grilled Lime
description: Juicy, smoky grilled beef koftas are seasoned with a bold Thai spice blend, served with a zippy mango-cucumber slaw and a squeeze of grilled lime. This summer, prepare yourself for the ultimate combo of savoury, fresh and tangy all in one meal!

Ingredients: Ground beef • Mangos • Coleslaw mix (carrot, green cabbage, red cabbage) • Cucumber • Limes • Sweet chili sauce (sugars (sugar, glucose), water, modified corn starch, apple cider vinegar, vinegar, chili peppers, salt, ginger, dehydrated red bell pepper, spices, dried garlic, crushed chilies, soybean oil, natural flavour, xanthan gum, acetic acid, citric acid, canola oil, paprika oleoresin, natural paprika flavour, caramel, potassium sorbate, sodium benzoate, calcium disodium EDTA) • Peanuts • Panko breadcrumbs (bleached wheat flour, yeast, sugar, salt) (wheat) • Rice vinegar (rice vinegar, sugar, salt) • Thai spice blend (salt, spices (including mustard) and herbs, sugars (sugar, corn syrup solids), dehydrated vegetables (onion, garlic), corn starch, coconut powder (coconut milk, maltodextrin, sodium caseinate (milk)), lemon juice powder (corn syrup solids, concentrated lemon juice, lemon oil, silicon dioxide), coconut oil, yeast extract, silicon dioxide) (mustard, milk).
